{
  "texts": [
    "The same applies after increasing the number of epochs to 20 and beyond if warranted.",
    "In the context of this study and the task at hand, the BERT model exhibits robust results after 20 epochs, particularly considering the low value for the loss.",
    "However, ELECTRA evidently requires a higher number of epochs to yield improved results.",
    "The BERT model has been identified as exhibiting the most promising accuracy results across all conducted steps.",
    "Consequently, it has been chosen for a conclusive real test, and the ensuing results are presented."
  ]
